{
  "stem": "17299.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 83.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since there was no corpsman or anyone to help him to stop the bleeding, we tore off the sleeves from his shirt and put that on his arms to stop the bleeding.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we had to keep on working, because Polish prisoners, German capos, and the-- and even the Wehrmacht were very abusive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When we marched back in the evening into-- into the Kaiserwald, we got stopped by [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Hanner, ?] Hans Brunn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said we have to work on foundation for the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we told him, we have to take him in-- in the hospital, because the bleeding did not stop entirely, severely injured.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said, you better leave him here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can take care better of him than they can in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We said, nothing doing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we took him to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'm very sorry to say we should have listened to Hans Brunn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We took him to the hospital, and we saw him back a few hours later.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we did not recognize his face anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "A couple of days later, he started talking with us, when we put-- were brought in-- couple of Polish prisoners were in charge there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They took off the bandages we had made for him, the shirt sleeves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they said it has to be stitched up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They did not give him anything for the pain, or anaesthesia, or something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Somebody put his-- stretch out his arm, and other one took his head in a hammerlock, and then they started stitching up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And every time he started moving or screaming, he would get a fist in his teeth from the Polish prisoners.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Once they had finished with him, then there were two NCOs, SS NCOs, in the-- in the-- hospital.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
